            "description": "Get list of videos from a YouTube channel.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `channelUrl` (required): Full YouTube channel URL\n- `maxVideos` (optional): Maximum number of videos to retrieve (default: 50)\n\n**Response:**\n- `success`: Boolean indicating success\n- `videos`: Array of video objects containing:\n  - `id`: YouTube video ID\n  - `title`: Video title\n  - `thumbnail`: Thumbnail URL\n  - `channelName`: Channel name\n- `channelName`: Name of the channel\n- `error`: Error message if failed"
